<field name="name">

&lt;P&gt;
wait - wait for any child process to die

&lt;P&gt;
&lt;HR&gt;
</field>
<field name="synopsis">

&lt;P&gt;
wait

&lt;P&gt;
&lt;HR&gt;
</field>
<field name="description">

&lt;P&gt;
Waits for a child process to terminate and returns the pid of the deceased
process, or &lt;CODE&gt;-1&lt;/CODE&gt; if there are no child processes. The status is returned in &lt;CODE&gt;$?&lt;/CODE&gt;.

&lt;HR&gt;
</field>
